articles.title: US Intelligence Shows Hamas Attack On Israel Surprised Iran: Report - NDTV
articles.description: The United States has collected intelligence showing that key Iranian leaders were surprised by the unprecedented attacks on Israel by Palestinian group Hamas in Israel, the New York Times reported on Wednesday, citing American officials.
articles.content:
Hamas' attack on Israel has killed over 1,200 people
